text:
and the prices are very competitive. Sixity offers a comprehensive range of parts and accessories, all good quality. I live on the west coast and like to support merchants from this geographical area. Particularly when they do such a great job.
I made purchases from Sixity directly and through Amazon, each time rewarded with expeditious shipping at no cost. Purchased timing belt kit, spark plugs and wire set at great prices.
I'll be back
